---
layout: base.njk
title: Notes on Practice
description: Essays, ideas, and observations on guitar practice, technique, and long-term musical development.
permalink: /notes/
---
<header class="notes-header">
  <h1>Notes on Practice</h1>
  <p>Essays, ideas, and observations on guitar practice, technique, and long-term musical development.</p>
</header>
<ul class="notes-list">
  {% for essay in collections.essays %}
  <li class="notes-list-item">
    <a href="{{ essay.url }}">
      <h2>{{ essay.data.title }}</h2>
      {% if essay.data.summary %}<p>{{ essay.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
      <span class="meta">{{ essay.date | monthYear }}</span>
    </a>
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
